New features include:
- You can click on the dashboard tiles (top goalscorer, assister, and POM) to see a filtered view of all players, not just the top three.
- Team and Player stats can now be filtered by match type (All, League, Trophy, Friendly).
- Managers can edit team lineups after a match to correct mistakes if necessary.
- Coaches can upload training session documents as well as adding a link to the session.
- A match in progress can now be more easily found
Enjoy!